{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "6fef95c9-4c4f-4dc2-8b55-knowflow-v1",
    "name": "KnowFlow V1",
    "description": "KnowFlow V1 接口测试集合。建议先按 01 -> 09 的顺序执行。注意：SSE 在 Postman 中可发起请求，但流式体验通常不如 curl。",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080"
    },
    {
      "key": "user_id",
      "value": "demo-user"
    },
    {
      "key": "session_id",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "document_id",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "source_name",
      "value": "backend-interview-notes.md"
    },
    {
      "key": "raw_content",
      "value": "# Go 后端面试笔记\n\nKnowFlow 的主链路是文档摄取、混合检索、Rerank、引用式回答、Redis 会话记忆、知识反写与索引热更新。\n\n混合检索采用 PgVector 语义召回和 pg_trgm 关键词召回，再用 RRF 融合，并在融合结果上做 Rerank。\n\nRedis 会话记忆采用 recent + summary 双层结构，超过阈值后会压缩历史消息。"
    },
    {
      "key": "question",
      "value": "总结一下 KnowFlow 的亮点"
    },
    {
      "key": "knowledge_content",
      "value": "KnowFlow 将知识反写落到结构化 knowledge_entries，再触发受影响范围的索引更新，而不是直接把内容追加到 markdown 文件。"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01-健康检查",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/healthz",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "healthz"
          ]
        }
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('健康检查返回 200', function () {",
              "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "02-上传文档-原始文本",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "X-User-ID",
            "value": "{{user_id}}",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "formdata",
          "formdata": [
            {
              "key": "source_name",
              "value": "{{source_name}}",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "key": "content",
              "value": "{{raw_content}}",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/kb/documents",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "kb",
            "documents"
          ]
        }
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('上传文档返回 200', function () {",
              "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
              "});",
              "var json = pm.response.json();",
              "if (json.DocumentID) {",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('document_id', json.DocumentID);",
              "}"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "03-上传文档-文件模式",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "X-User-ID",
            "value": "{{user_id}}",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "formdata",
          "formdata": [
            {
              "key": "file",
              "type": "file",
              "src": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/kb/documents",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "kb",
            "documents"
          ]
        }
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "04-普通问答",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "X-User-ID",
            "value": "{{user_id}}",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"session_id\": \"{{session_id}}\",\n  \"message\": \"{{question}}\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/chat/query",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "chat",
            "query"
          ]
        }
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('普通问答返回 200', function () {",
              "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
              "});",
              "var json = pm.response.json();",
              "if (json.session_id) {",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('session_id', json.session_id);",
              "}",
              "pm.test('返回 answer 字段', function () {",
              "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('answer');",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "05-流式问答-SSE",
